#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/capture.adoc:63
msgid ""
"For this activity, you will complete an exercise simulating data capture.  "
"You will begin to work with https://dwc.tdwg.org/terms/[Darwin Core terms^] "
"and make decisions on data that is needed for your organization/project and "
"you will consider which of that data will be shared later during publication."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/capture.adoc:66
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:40
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/publishing.adoc:62
msgid "Read the Practice Use Case (if you haven't already)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/capture.adoc:68
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-herbarium-specimens.adoc:54
msgid ""
"Imagine that you are the person assigned to transcribe the data found on the "
"herbarium sheets."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/capture.adoc:71
msgid ""
"Download xref:attachment$UC1-2-base-material.zip[UC1-2-base-material.zip,"
"opts=download]. (34.4 MB). There are 10 images. Two images per specimen for "
"a total of five specimens.  The herbarium sheets are in Spanish (data may "
"come to you in various means and in other languages than your own), but you "
"should be able to recognize the data contained in the fields on the labels. "
"Remember to use both images per record to compile the information."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/capture.adoc:72
msgid ""
"Download the spreadsheet template: xref:attachment$UC1-2-occurrence-template."
"xlsx[UC1-2-occurrence-template.xlsx,opts=download] (57.3 KB) to transcribe "
"the information found on each of the images for the five specimens."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/capture.adoc:73
msgid ""
"Download xref:attachment$UC1-Herbarium-Exercise_EN.docx[UC1-Herbarium-"
"Exercise_EN.docx,opts=download] to provide your answers."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/capture.adoc:75
msgid ""
"you may need to add fields to the spreadsheet as you may be able to capture "
"more information from the labels than was planned for in the template."
msgstr ""

